name: 人生の鍵 - THE KEY TO LIFE
description:
Some people believe in their courage and their efforts to get to their achievements and some belief in pure luck.

there is a famous Japanese saying that,
"私たちは自分の運を作ります"
which means,
" We create our own luck"
that thought drives me to make this wonderful Piece!
In this artwork, what I represent is that the girl who in the bottom, does not believe(doubtful) in things that bring luck to her life.
the things on her head are "Maneki Neko", "Emas", "Daruma Doll", "Shrine" which all represent Luck.
